blog.name: sailor-rose-princess
blog.title: The Rosiest Rose
blog.description:
My main blog. Nonbinary - she/her and they/them pronouns - bisexual - birthday June 30th 1995 - adhd, depression, anxiety, BPD, synesthesia - Artist, sews outfits, Build a Bear enthusiast, and proud owner of the Lazytown Build a Bears. Often posts stuff from fandoms (mostly anime, Sailor Moon, Lazytown, Rocky Horror, Bob's Burgers, Homestuck, Disney, Hello Kitty, South Park, Captain Underpants, Samurai Jack, FLCL, Pee-wee Herman among others), recipes, cute stuff, fairy kei/lolita/j-fashion, mental health, body positivity, LGBT stuff (mostly try to stay on the positive side). Sometimes I take selfies and/or cosplays, or post art. I also like sewing Build a Bear outfits. My boyfriend is Nick aka des-rookie. Fair warning, I'm not a spoiler free blog, but I will tag stuff for spoilers.  Also if you want a certain trigger tagged, don't hesitate to ask me, I do my best to tag triggers, but if I miss something, let me know.  
Spoil me here:  http://www.amazon.com/registry/wishlist/2D7JUAKQ1ZPWH

summary: Do you want a Long Furby?  Do you not have the sewing skills make one yourself?  Would you like something a little different and...
body:
Long Furby Sale’s Post

Do you want a Long Furby? Do you not have the sewing skills make one yourself? Would you like something a little different and unique and made just for you? Or do you simply like the style I made for my long Furbies Cupcakes and Axel and would like a cute Long Furby in my style?

I’m now opening 3 slots for custom requests for homemade long Furbies made by me.

- Each long Furb will be completely unique, no two are exactly alike, so each one you get will be one of a kind.

- I have two styles and two sizes, breadstick style, and worm style. Breadstick style, shown by blue Axel here, is a chubbier, shorter, more huggable style Furby. Worm style, shown by pastel Cupcakes, is longer and more ropey, great for wrapping around things.

- Cost of each Long Furby

$50 for small (3 feet for Breadstick style, 3 and a half feet for Worm style)

$75 for Extra Long (5 feet for Breadstick style, 6 feet for Worm style)

- These extras are available

Doll armature $15

“Heartbeat” sound effect $10

Scent pad $5 (currently available scents - candy surprise, fresh cut flowers, thin mints, sugar and sparkle, vanilla cupcake, cotton candy, strawberry, popcorn, pizza, berry blast, lavender, bubblegum, marshmallow, pumpkin)

- You can pick up to 3 main colors per Furby, have whatever eye style or expression you want. Angry punk, kawaii anime-ish, silly and cartoony, creepy cute, you decide. Normally I do Furby beaks as yellow, but if you want a different color, don’t hesitate to tell me.

- For now, I’ll ship orders in the US, but later I might be open to international order. I’m just starting out don’t forget. Shipping cost extra, especially depending on where you live. I’m gonna estimate on average, 10 to 15 dollars.

- I’d prefer if I get payment before working on your Furby. Once I get payed, I start shopping for materials to make the Furbies with (some of the extras, being bought online, will slightly delay the start of the project). However, one I actually start sewing the Furby itself, I can’t refund anything.

- I’ll open 3 slots for now, first come first serve basis. But if you miss your chance this time, don’t fret, as I’ll open more in the future.

- If you have any questions, don’t hesitate to ask me.

Slots Currently Open:

1.

2.

3.

IF YOU CANT BUY, AT LEAST REBLOG PLEASE!
